1781089908587186	bob	itc:v3:AWKSc8kyZJPJk5EAAAAAQau9WtV610AAAAEzpQI		item.update	bn-8zqz	{"field":"description","value":"After an agent manually resolved committed conflict markers and committed: 'maw ws conflicts <ws>' said 'No conflicts found / 1 workspace(s) can be merged cleanly', but 'maw ws merge <ws> --into default --check' BLOCKED with '1 unresolved conflict(s)' and 'maw ws resolve --list' agreed with the blocker ('1 structured conflict, sides=[epoch, ws]') — while the file itself contained zero markers. An extra 'maw ws sync' printed 'Cleared stale conflict metadata after a manual resolution commit' and unblocked the merge. Seen twice in one session (two different workspaces). The three commands should read the same source of truth, and a manual resolution commit should clear the metadata without requiring a follow-up sync."}	blake3:77VNP4termrazPT4anrWNxfP4Z1m-2Z_sy1AiFNW6HY
