1781089917519832	bob	itc:v3:AWKSc8kyZJPJk5EAAAAAQau9WtV610AAAAEzqgI		item.update	bn-21cj	{"field":"description","value":"Observed in sigil repo: 'maw ws sync <ws>' printed 'Rebase complete: 1 commit(s) replayed cleanly' but had actually written a whole-file structured diff3 conflict (with '# structured conflict at src/run_cli.rs' header) into the file and committed it to the workspace HEAD. The agent only discovered it because a later build failed. 'Replayed cleanly' must never be printed when conflict content was committed; the summary line should match what maw ws resolve --list reports."}	blake3:R73FSv7DXr6gNU4_vijIsFEd9aUWQBYzuvphwza66fY
