1781093396152699	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy3xI		item.comment	bn-1abp	{"body":"Merged to main 5c3f726c: auto-rebase writes one-time notice consumed by next maw exec; stale-epoch warning latched to once per invocation; ws diff defaults to epoch; create --from divergence NOTE; better outside-repo error; deprecated --rebase form purged from maw-owned text; AGENTS.md template documents auto-rebase + --no-auto-rebase. Combined just check green."}	blake3:BXbmOy8aoP4pTbX9fB5EkBawNtJJA1NHXN_-ZTNoF4g
