1781100468946910	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy7RI		item.comment	bn-6xpz	{"body":"Fix complete. Commit df8e8819 in workspace bn-6xpz. All tests green (just check). Summary: (1) report_cleared_stale_sidecar now returns EffectiveConflictState; (2) sync() no-op path checks is_conflicted() and prints conflict count+paths+resolve hint; (3) rebase.rs fast-forward path also checks; (4) print_conflict_guidance updated — trailing 'maw ws sync' step removed since bn-8zqz auto-clears on next maw command. New tests: sync_up_to_date_but_conflicted_workspace_reports_conflict + sync_up_to_date_clean_workspace_prints_up_to_date."}	blake3:mpTjEoBYREGcwd-1ouXJBPFJXoRtSQt2UUPoGimaikU
1781100537114243	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy7hI		item.comment	bn-1olb	{"body":"DONE. Fix committed as b5f82acc in workspace bn-1olb. just check passes (all test suites green, 0 failures). Summary: introduced AgainstMode::StaleAwareEpoch for the no-flag default; resolve_stale_aware_epoch picks base by priority: (1) workspace's refs/manifold/epoch/ws/<name>, (2) git merge-base fallback, (3) current epoch. Prints NOTE to stderr when stale path taken. Explicit --against epoch always = current epoch. 3 new integration tests added."}	blake3:wuDbIdU7PUkgr8uANJ0EUvpyfnzD6UY74B2aqlagSfo
1781101094338638	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy7xI		item.comment	bn-1nwn	{"body":"Fix complete. Commit 57a2c5ac in workspace bn-1nwn. Summary: --keep epoch and --keep both now use per-hunk 3-way merge instead of whole-blob replace. --keep epoch uses ConflictResolution::Ours (epoch wins conflict hunks, ws disjoint edits preserved). --keep both uses ConflictResolution::Union (both sides' conflict lines included, clean regions merged). Per-hunk path activates for Conflict::Content with 2 sides + non-None base + text blobs; binary/N>2/AddAdd/ModifyDelete/missing-base fall back to legacy blob behavior. 5 new tests added. just check passes (all test suites green)."}	blake3:qoiRT4Gl4wWPH9wti6zcjxMOSZSZz6dzaHPd6jSjEpg
1781101593412405	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy8BI		item.comment	bn-6xpz	{"body":"Merged ffed522a: sync up-to-date + fast-forward paths consult effective_conflict_state and report residual committed conflicts; post-resolve guidance no longer teaches the trailing 'maw ws sync'. Verified in /tmp repro. Combined just check green."}	blake3:bUoOMqfSE40muAKn7Dzr0uFh16LzeOk9L9dc3ZMbl68
