1781101593697390	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy9BI		item.comment	bn-1nwn	{"body":"Merged 7c40c398: --keep epoch (Ours) and --keep both (Union) re-run the gix text driver per conflicted hunk, preserving cleanly-merged edits; binary/N>2/no-base fall back to whole-blob. Verified in /tmp: disjoint edit survives keep-epoch. Combined just check green."}	blake3:Y1eZBs22VsBJHpg6H6TMe5Xfbf4FVD-3fRz5ejaeAtw
