1781104995826619	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyihM		item.comment	bn-566k	{"body":"Merged 335acf3b: promote_overlaps_to_conflicts 'None => continue' hole now installs Conflict::ModifyDelete (deleter=epoch, modifier=ws) for epoch-delete vs ws-modify AND ws-re-add; --keep epoch deletes, --keep ws restores; reverse direction unchanged. Combined just check green (after repairing a union-resolution test-file break — see follow-up bone on sanity-checking resolve output)."}	blake3:482IrCVKGav-vwLQUu-Q4D4lrOlVNfjtK_uA2YyU-I0
