1781109824986323	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEypBM		item.comment	bn-1mn0	{"body":"Merged (post-f4a6e6f9): reconstruction sets base_content via ConflictSide::with_base; effective_base_oid helper unifies all three keep-path guards (side.base_content || Content.base); no-base whole-blob fallback now warns for epoch/both too. Verified end-to-end in /tmp: reconstruction + per-hunk keep-epoch preserves disjoint edits. Root just check green."}	blake3:eceEyPQrm0b_EqwYWOp_cEmmArNbA82ysKpRBzCd2JU
