1781117444927914	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyvRM		item.comment	bn-1s8d	{"body":"DONE (f6ac94a0). Root cause: clean.rs used backend.exists() which always returns false for 'default' in consolidated layout (workspaces-dir lookup, but default IS the repo root). Fix: layout-aware resolution via LayoutFlavor::detect_with_env + default_target_path — resolves to repo root in consolidated. clean --all now also includes root target/. Harmful 'Fix: maw ws create default' hint removed. Tests: ws_clean_default_consolidated_cleans_root_target, ws_clean_default_consolidated_no_target_ok, ws_clean_all_consolidated_includes_root, ws_clean_missing_named_workspace_no_create_hint — all pass."}	blake3:0gNaqha40ErGQs1yIZywrSH4ribW_ize1I-ihrr4LSc
1781117452653110	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyvhM		item.comment	bn-21qy	{"body":"DONE (f6ac94a0). Root cause: create CLI arm had no reserved-name check; destroy() had a blanket 'Cannot destroy default' bail that blocked impostor cleanup. Fixes: (1) workspace/mod.rs CLI dispatch arm now refuses name 'default' with 'reserved' error before source check or backend — internal callers (restore/recover/changes) unaffected. (2) destroy() detects consolidated impostor: if .maw/workspaces/default exists, routes to destroy_consolidated_impostor_default() which uses git worktree remove + fs fallback, prints impostor message, never touches repo root. (3) v2-bare legacy init path confirmed working (maw init --legacy-ws still creates ws/default/). Tests: ws_create_default_refused_with_from_in_consolidated, ws_create_default_refused_bare_in_consolidated, ws_create_default_refused_in_v2, ws_destroy_default_removes_impostor_in_consolidated, ws_destroy_default_refuses_when_no_impostor_consolidated, ws_destroy_default_refuses_in_v2, maw_init_legacy_ws_creates_default_workspace — all pass."}	blake3:Iwa2fdEfuGCZiFvONVp_zLnwFiL-xkoG7cvJKne7jjA
1781117752210519	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEyvxM		item.comment	bn-1s8d	{"body":"Merged: ws clean resolves the default workspace via LayoutFlavor::default_target_path (repo root in consolidated); clean --all includes root; harmful create-hint removed. Live-verified. Root just check green."}	blake3:O--j_Y0F5Skst7N3SWszLK_YJmJF-UKXlQ6uohBUyKs
