1781310524368887	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy0RM		item.comment	bn-1qtj	{"body":"Merged: epoch-ref write retried + loud with copy-pasteable fix; stale-by-ref self-heal in backend list/status (ancestry-guarded). Live-verified: desynced ref repaired silently, genuine stale unchanged. The worker's own commit 4be34a20 was ORPHANED by a concurrent agent's merge mid-cycle (live recurrence of the sigil incident) — recovered via cherry-pick; forensics in bn-20sa."}	blake3:x3eoSUHQIZVWoByCQvYKQ-cBhvksznwAJGHEc48Lj-w
