1781310573867185	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy1RM		item.comment	bn-20sa	{"body":"Starting work on bn-20sa: set_head never-abandon guard + reflog trail + oplog visibility. Will implement 4 parts: (1) guard at rebase set_head, (2) root-cause investigation, (3) reflog trail, (4) oplog visibility."}	blake3:3RPivy0DWTs0x8veLmd1w87xnTE9uLtHaZnxNMzfXQg
1781311896992447	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy1hM		item.comment	bn-20sa	{"body":"DONE: Implemented all 4 parts of bn-20sa. Commit a90c8ab5. Guard logic: CAS check (HEAD moved since walk) + non-consumed-work check (replayed==0 while head_git!=old_git, checked via is_ancestor). Refusal text names SHAs and remediation. Reflog entry format: '<old> <new> maw <maw@localhost> <ts> +0000\\tmaw: set_head (rebase)\\n'. Oplog entry: OpPayload::Rebase{old_epoch,new_epoch,old_head,new_head,replayed,conflicts,trigger}. Root cause: unprovable definitively; guard makes all variants loud. Tests: 5 in tests/rebase_never_abandon_bn_20sa.rs, all pass. just check: fully green."}	blake3:AGWEfzCghlRoS14wmFm85tfBULoFv9fYO05gJ5wQ-Kg
1781312245201317	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy1xM		item.comment	bn-20sa	{"body":"Merged: never-abandon guard at rebase set_head (CAS on walk-start HEAD + non-consumed-work refusal with is_ancestor escape; SAFETY ABORT names SHAs + remediation); maw-git set_head now appends a HEAD reflog entry (both live incidents were forensically blind without it); OpPayload::Rebase oplog entries from ff + replay paths with trigger context (sync/sync-all/auto-rebase:merge(sources)). Empty-walk root cause not definitively proven — the guard makes every variant loud. Root just check green. The orphan class is now guarded at all three writer sites (checkout ff: bn-29z8; exec auto-sync: bn-29z8; rebase set_head: bn-20sa)."}	blake3:5AHgcDId2qF8_vilanA5GcNSI3hFBLH6nyfA9jC3CqA
