1781372690706745	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy3RM		item.comment	bn-8flz	{"body":"Starting implementation: creating workspace bn-8flz and beginning audit of all HEAD-moving paths per the design. Will implement in order: (1) maw-git native methods, (2) safety choke-point shared dispatch, (3) retire shell-outs, (4) tests."}	blake3:Eb13dVnzKurnOZ5M80X45isNHqHmQeBwOiaU1Du4Njw
1781375145546772	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy3hM		item.comment	bn-8flz	{"body":"Worker done: native HEAD-move choke-point + retire checkout shell-outs. Commits: 41b711ea (feat: native choke-point, retire shell-outs), 1c33c7cf (test: regression tests), 288bc09e (fix: clippy + test rebase semantics). just check: 30 test suites all green. Key deliverables: (1) GixRepo::checkout_detach/checkout_to_branch/checkout_force methods + set_head_to_branch in maw-git; (2) advance.rs now detects committed-ahead work and routes through rebase_workspace (not checkout_to); (3) sync/checks.rs shell-out removed; working_copy.rs checkout_to/checkout_force nativized; merge.rs force_checkout_fallback nativized; checkout_epoch dead function deleted; (4) 6 integration tests in advance_orphan_regression_bn_8flz.rs covering: orphan regression (acceptance), clean fast-forward, already-at-epoch noop, sync fast-forward native path, sync rebase preservation, grep-style no-shell-out guard."}	blake3:nK1sqRvuIJoL63jMeJlcRe3OlBihgYj16Pje7Ph8uQw
1781375560488130	maw-dev	itc:v3:AWKTmSTM_JOSSTQAAAAAQa7Vbfq6qsAAAAEy3xM		item.comment	bn-8flz	{"body":"Merged to main. Native HEAD-move choke-point: checkout_detach/checkout_to_branch/checkout_force in maw-git (all reflog-writing); advance now routes committed-ahead work through the guarded rebase path instead of stash-only checkout — orphan FIXED. Live-verified all 5 acceptance criteria against the worker binary: (1) advance preserves committed-ahead work rebased onto new epoch (in HEAD tree + on disk, honest 'advanced with rebase' msg); (2) clean ff advance works; (3) sync ff native, HEAD==epoch; (4) merge reattaches default-ws to ref: refs/heads/main; (5) rebase path still yields structured conflicts. No production git-checkout HEAD-mover shell-out remains (4 grep hits all in #[cfg(test)]); dead checkout_epoch deleted; stale TODO(gix) removed. Root just check + DST 5/5 green. Orphan-commit class now closed at the SOURCE — one native guarded primitive, all paths routed through it."}	blake3:UXOQ6zMKGvfMiJf9PUnYkRIokhopgSbtV-GWBuBnqrc
